Rayquaza (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0383: Groudon
Pokémon
#0385: Jirachi →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Rayquaza (TCG Pocket).

Rayquaza has been featured on 37 different cards since it debuted in the EX Dragon expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Rayquaza cards are normally Colorless-type or Dragon-type Basic Pokémon. As a Dragon-type, their attacks normally have costs including and Energy.
